OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776690659
OL,3,CPeople forced to suffer due to public
OL,4,Ctoilet 'deserts', health leaders warn
OL,6,FPeople are forced to suffer due to
OL,7,Fpublic toilet "deserts"across England,
OL,8,Fhealth leaders have warned.
OL,10,FNew analysis by the Royal Society for
OL,11,FPublic Health (RSPH) found a
OL,12,F"significant shortfall" in the number
OL,13,Fof public toilets across the country,
OL,14,Fwith facilities dropping by 14% since
OL,15,F2016.
OL,17,FIts calculations, shared with the
OL,18,FPress Association, suggest there are
OL,19,Fnow 15,481 people for every public
OL,20,Ftoilet in England.
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@WO]tD@AOUtD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
