CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776690659
OL,3,CPeople forced to suffer due to public
OL,4,Ctoilet 'deserts', health leaders warn
OL,6,FThe data is based on more than 200
OL,7,FFreedom of Information (FOI) requests
OL,8,Fto councils in charge of providing
OL,9,Fpublic toilets.
OL,11,FThe RSPH warned that a lack of toilets
OL,12,Fincreases the number of people who
OL,13,Fthen urinate in public, creating
OL,14,Funhygienic conditions.
OL,16,FIt also pointed to a potential knock-
OL,17,Fon effect for local businesses after
OL,18,Fits research suggested some people
OL,19,Favoid going out due to a lack of
OL,20,Fpublic facilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776690659
OL,3,CPeople forced to suffer due to public
OL,4,Ctoilet 'deserts', health leaders warn
OL,6,FOther people restrict their fluid
OL,7,Fintake ` risking dehydration, the RSPH
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FWilliam Roberts, chief executive of
OL,11,Fthe RSPH, said: "Access to public
OL,12,Ftoilets is a universal need that we
OL,13,Fall have, and we shouldn't shy away
OL,14,Ffrom talking about it.
OL,16,F"One public toilet for per 15,000
OL,17,Fpeople simply isn't good enough and,
OL,18,Fwithout action, that figure will keep
OL,19,Frising as we lose more facilities.
OL,26,@sD@QOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776690659
OL,3,CPeople forced to suffer due to public
OL,4,Ctoilet 'deserts', health leaders warn
OL,6,F"For some people, access to a public
OL,7,Ftoilet can be the difference as to
OL,8,Fwhether they leave the house, for
OL,9,Fothers it can lead to deliberately
OL,10,Frestricting fluid intake to avoid the
OL,11,Fneeding to use a toilet.
OL,13,F"The effects also go far beyond the
OL,14,Findividual. Having an insufficient
OL,15,Fnumber of public toilets has
OL,16,Finevitable unsanitary consequences,
OL,17,Fcreating unpleasant environments that
OL,18,Fdegrade our public realm.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776690659
OL,3,CPeople forced to suffer due to public
OL,4,Ctoilet 'deserts', health leaders warn
OL,6,F"As a country we can and should be
OL,7,Fdoing better. We need to create public
OL,8,Fspaces that people want to spend time
OL,9,Fin, and this means giving local
OL,10,Fauthorities the resources they need to
OL,11,Fprovide the facilities we all rely on."
OL,13,FTo help boost the number of public
OL,14,Ftoilets, the RSPH is calling for new
OL,15,Fstrategic authorities to have a duty
OL,16,Fto ensure there are sufficient public
OL,17,Ftoilets in the places people go,
OL,18,Fsupported by funding from central
OL,19,FGovernment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776690659
OL,3,CPeople forced to suffer due to public
OL,4,Ctoilet 'deserts', health leaders warn
OL,6,FIt also said developers must do more,
OL,7,Fcalling for regulations that would
OL,8,Frequire public toilets to be included
OL,9,Fin any development that includes non-
OL,10,Fresidential units.
OL,12,FAt present, local councils get to
OL,13,Fdecide on how many toilets are needed
OL,14,Fin their area.
OL,16,FAccording to the RSPH, since 2016
OL,17,Fthere has been a 14% overall reduction
OL,18,Fin public toilets across England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
