OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776690659
OL,3,CPeople forced to suffer due to public
OL,4,Ctoilet 'deserts', health leaders warn
OL,6,FIn devolved nations the situation is
OL,7,Fbetter, with around 8,500 people per
OL,8,Fpublic toilet in Scotland and 6,748 in
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FA spokesman for the Local Government
OL,12,FAssociation said: "The lack of public
OL,13,Ftoilets can disproportionately affect
OL,14,Fvulnerable groups, including older
OL,15,Fpeople, people with disabilities,
OL,16,Fthose with medical conditions, babies
OL,17,Fand children and people that find
OL,18,Fthemselves sleeping rough.
OL,26,@tD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
