OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776690659
OL,3,CPeople forced to suffer due to public
OL,4,Ctoilet 'deserts', health leaders warn
OL,6,FA spokesman for the Ministry of
OL,7,FHousing, Communities and Local
OL,8,FGovernment said: "To help councils
OL,9,Fprovide public services like toilets
OL,10,Fwe've made over #78 billion available
OL,11,Ffor council finances, with local
OL,12,Fleaders free to decide for themselves
OL,13,Fhow best to spend the majority of
OL,14,Fthis."
OL,16,FThe RSPH figure of 15,481 people is
OL,17,Fbased on FOI responses from 221 of 309
OL,18,Flocal authorities in England.
OL,26,@pD@ROUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
