OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776690659
OL,3,CPeople forced to suffer due to public
OL,4,Ctoilet 'deserts', health leaders warn
OL,6,FIt said 47 million people live in
OL,7,Fthese areas (roughly 82% of the
OL,8,Fpopulation).
OL,10,FCouncils were asked for the number of
OL,11,Fpublic toilets in their area in 2016
OL,12,Fand 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
